ing and discretionary and brokerage services import and export documentary collections and guarantee services liquidity management and wealth solutions and risk management services as well as internet mobile telephone and branch banking services the company serves small enterprises government and corporate and institutional clients as well as high net worth individuals and families as of december   it operated  branches in the united kingdom and  located in the isle of man and the channel islands the company was founded in  and is based in london the united kingdom hsbc bank plc is a subsidiary of hsbc holdings plc detailed description  canada squarelondon  e hqunited kingdomfounded in  employees phone     wwwhsbccouk key executives for hsbc bank plc mr antonio p simoes ceo  director age  d watts chief financial officer james alasdair emmett chief operating officer mr stuart thomson gulliver group chief executive officer of hsbc uk age  d k sheehan chief executive officer of hsbc private bank uk limited age  compensation as of fiscal year  hsbc bank plc key developments hsbc bank presents at st petersburg international economic forum  programme jun  pm jun   hsbc bank presents at st petersburg international economic forum  programme jun  pm venue st petersburg russia speakers robin phillips cohead of global banking aryzta appoints hsbc for strategic review of investment in picard may   aryzta ag swxaryn appointed hsbc bank plc as its advisers in relation to an evaluation of alternatives for its  investment in picard groupe sas hsbc bank presents at th annual latin american energy  infrastructure finance forum mar  pm mar   hsbc bank presents at th annual latin american energy  infrastructure finance forum mar  pm venue the ritzcarlton south beach  lincoln road miami beach florida united states speakers raphael dumas director similar private companies by industry company name region abbey national bank plc europe airdrie savings bank limited europe akcb finance ltd e