’ve also included an extension to allow you to search sme lending products by product segment commercial credit cards ccc products you can request information about the commercial credit cards available from hsbc in the uk we’ve also included an extension to allow you to search for commercial credit cards by product segment product information for other countries is currently unavailable who can use them use of the apis and any related data is subject to the terms of the open licence and subject to terms and conditions how much do they cost there are no charges for using these apis you dont have to register documentation and sandbox  key features name of each product product features eligibility description pricing fees and interest rates open banking apis for hsbc first direct and ms bank hsbc group developer portal the definitive source of information and technical specifications for the apis made available by members of the hsbc group including hsbc uk first direct and ms bank public websites this website is for software developers if you think you are on the wrong site please visit the relevant public website open banking apis open banking apis are free to use and provide uptodate information about the location and facilities of our branches and atms detailed product information for personal and business current accounts lending to small to medium enterprises and commercial credit cardsyou can use this data to build applications that make it easier for personal and business customers to compare what’s offered by different banks the data provided through the associated apis relates to the uk only and is prepared to the open api data format and security standards as maintained by the open banking implementation entity obie branch locator get the locations of and facilities at our branches atm locator get the locations of all our atms product finder current accounts sme lending products and commercial credit cards branch locator get the locations of and facilities 