so get your card unblocked if there are no issues online banking video guide see how our services are performing find out more see how our services are performing find out more search our help topics mobile  online banking security centre find a branch lost  stolen cards settling in the uk money worries moving abroad card support complaints  feedback bereavement closing an account inactive accounts havent found what youre looking for tweet us hsbcukhelp this link will open in a new browser windowcontact us existing customers    lines are open am to pm every day  hours a day if you are an hsbc advance customer find a specific department this link will open in a new browser window textphone contact numbers this link will open in a new browser window cysylltwch âr gwasanaeth iaith gymraeg   neu   maer llinellau ar agor yb i yh bob dydd ac eithrio dydd nadolig gŵyl san steffan a dydd calan maen bosib caiff galwadau eu harolygu aneu recordio nonhsbc customers    lines are open am to pm everyday except christmas day boxing day and new years day from outside the uk     javascript is currently disabled on this computerdevice as such cookies for this site are disabled to log on to online banking and have access to all the features of our fullyoptimised website please enable your javascript settings via your browser for a list of all the cookies and what they do please read our cookie policy back to top help  support find a branch join the conversation products  services current accounts saving accounts credit cards loans mortgages international services investing insurance online banking read more about online banking hsbc mobile banking app register in app to start using today read more about hsbc mobile banking app website feedback this link will open an overlay window help  support find a branch website feedback this link will open an overlay window everyday banking current accounts saving accounts credit cards international services switching to hsbc security centre card