fore you apply     how to apply for bank account did you know you could be eligible for our hsbc advance bank account with no monthly fee key features attractive rates  benefits across a wide range of hsbc products make atm cash withdrawals worldwide without hsbc nonsterling cash fees a nonsterling transaction fee of  still applies  customer service eligibility criteria please ensure you can answer yes to the following questions are you  years or over will you be paying in at least £ into your account each month or a minimum of £ every six months not including money transferred from any other sole or joint personal accounts you hold with hsbc bank no thanks find out more hsbc international services and products  hsbc bank uk skip page header and navigation personal business hsbc online banking activation were currently making improvements to our online banking service if you registered for online banking prior to the th december  its not possible for you to activate your existing secure key and you will need to restart your registration if you registered for online banking after this date please log on to online banking entering your username memorable answer and your password from here you will be prompted to activate your secure key we apologise for any inconvenience which this delay may cause once you are registered we look forward to introducing you to online banking including the exciting enhancements were working on now find out more site search enter search terms internet banking log on register everyday banking accounts  services skip to borrowing navigation current accounts hsbc premier account hsbc advance account hsbc student account bank account view all current accounts savings isas online bonus saver flexible saver view all savings accounts credit cards hsbc credit cards premier credit card student credit card view all credit cards international services hsbc currency account international payments travel money view all international services services 